summary: Hi just found out about you recently. I have a badly scarred pikachu that always puts mud and other things in its scar tissue is...
question: Hi just found out about you recently. I have a badly scarred pikachu that always puts mud and other things in its scar tissue is that normal? Also would it be best to get her some clothes or ribbon to keep her from getting mud all over I'm afraid she'll get a infection.
answer:
I’ve never heard of a rodent Pokémon like Pikachi using mud like that. They may occasionally lick scars, but using mud?

I’m pretty sure that Poké Marts carry special ointments for something like this. But to get her to stop with using the mud, a ribbon or two may help while you get her to try the ointment.

title: Elizabeth Cunnilingus the Third
body:
• Name: Elizabeth
  • Age: 25
  • Height: 5’7
  • Hair Color: Naturally Brunette but dyes it Blond
  • Eye color: Storm Grey
  • Skin Tone: Fair skin and light
  • Body type: Curvy hourglass.
  • Home Region: Sinnoh
  • Likes: The good life, new clothes, meeting new people, Sex, Pokephilia, being free of her Family, swimming, sour foods, feeling pleased.
  • Dislikes: Foul weather, having to put on an act, not being with her Pokemon, boring people, being called a dumb slut, being lost in the wild.
  • Dark Secret: Elizabeth is slowly raising up money to buy out her father company and ruin him for good.

Info: Elizabeth is a 25-year-old woman who grew up in a wealthy gem mining family. The eldest daughter of 3 Elizabeth grew up in a life of luxury and wealth with no worries to deal with. From the outside one would call her life perfect, fancy dresses, grand parties, meeting famous people and going all around the world on a dime. To the world, Elizabeth had it all but the truth was she was more of a prisoner than anything else.

Elizabeth felt she had no freedom to her life, she never once had any real choices in what she did or what she could do. Her father was very controlling and had his own plans for her. It wasn’t until Elizabeth was older that she found an escape in the form of webcasting.

At night Elizabeth had privacy and freedom and through the use of the internet stumble into the world of porn and webcamming. She soon became addicted to them and after a year built up the courage to try it herself. She loved it all, pretending to be someone else and allowing her true passions to be shown. She began to host shows and using the money she earns to buy sex toys and even taking request from her fans. She even started to bring pokephilia as well into her shows and that only added to her fan base. For the first time, life was wonderful until her father found out.

She father demanded she stop and start acting like a proper lady, he had plans for her and didn’t want her to be whoring herself out and ruin the family name. Elizabeth had enough and soon ran away from home. Her father cut her off from the family money in the hopes of making her come home but thanks to her web shows and even doing some photo shoots and movies Elizabeth was financially secure and finally free. She now travels around the world, doing local shows and shows and even a porn movie or two. She has no regrets about her life or what has become of it, instead, she is happy and enjoying life for the first time ever,

Her Team: Lopunny (Pompom) Arcanine (LordHowl) Rapidash (Deepflame) Garchomp (Shardtooth)  Gorebyss (PinkyShell) Mudsdale (Mudstomp)

Top kinks: Video recording, Public sex, Teasing, toys, Switch, Giving pleasure, prolong sex sessions, Soft Sex, Rough sex, Being Dominated Pokephilia
